* Highlight days with scheduled habits
* Click a date to see habits due that day and mark completion











| Component     | Purpose                                |
| ------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| `Box`, `Flex` | Layout containers                      |
| `Progress`    | XP bars and habit progress             |
| `Checkbox`    | Habit status                           |
| `Badge`       | Gamification badges                    |
| `Modal`       | Add/Edit Habit popup                   |
| `RadioGroup`  | Frequency selector                     |
| `Tabs`        | Switch between Today / Week / Calendar |
| `Tooltip`     | Hover-based detail popups              |
